overview:
Automatic Driveway Gates is a market leading access control and automatic driveway gate company.

We supply and install automatic gates, access control systems, gate openers, solar powered driveway gates, commercial and residential gates and much more. we are fully licensed and insured in each state we service. We have all in house employees and we do not use sub-contractors. We are a member of the BBB with an A+ standing and are also members of the American Fence Association.
